Hi Mark,

I hope you’re doing well. My name is [Your Name] and I lead partnership development at [Your Organization]. We’ve been following Helping Hands Charity’s work and are impressed by your impact in the community.

We’re currently looking to collaborate with like-minded nonprofits on initiatives that strengthen local support networks. After reviewing our internal “Partnership Opportunities” brief, I believe there is strong overlap in our goals—particularly around:
• Tiered sponsorship options that can fund community projects
• Opportunities for joint promotion to broaden both of our audiences
• Possibilities for staff volunteer days or co-hosted fundraising events

I would love to schedule a short call next week to learn more about Helping Hands’ priorities and explore how we can create a mutually beneficial partnership.

Could you let me know your availability over the next week or two? If there is someone else on your team I should loop in, please let me know.

Thank you for your time, and I look forward to the possibility of working together.

Best regards,
[Your Name]
[Your Title] | [Your Organization]
[Phone]
[Website]
